                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media tm-notification-item">
                        <div class="tm-gray-circle"><img src="~/Admin/img/notification-02.jpg" alt="Avatar Image" class="rounded-circle"></div>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <p class="mb-2">
                                <b>Oliver Too</b> and <b>6 others</b> sent you existing <a href="#"
                                                                                           class="tm-notification-link">product updates</a>. Read more reports.
                            </p>
                            <span class="tm-small tm-text-color-secondary">6h ago.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media tm-notification-item">
                        <div class="tm-gray-circle"><img src="~/Admin/img/notification-03.jpg" alt="Avatar Image" class="rounded-circle"></div>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <p class="mb-2">
                                <b>Victoria</b> and <b>6 others</b> sent you <a href="#"
                                                                                class="tm-notification-link">order updates</a>. Read order information.
                            </p>
                            <span class="tm-small tm-text-color-secondary">6h ago.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media tm-notification-item">
                        <div class="tm-gray-circle"><img src="~/Admin/img/notification-01.jpg" alt="Avatar Image" class="rounded-circle"></div>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <p class="mb-2">
                                <b>Laura Cute</b> and <b>6 others</b> sent you <a href="#"
                                                                                  class="tm-notification-link">product records</a>.
                            </p>
                            <span class="tm-small tm-text-color-secondary">6h ago.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media tm-notification-item">
                        <div class="tm-gray-circle"><img src="~/Admin/img/notification-02.jpg" alt="Avatar Image" class="rounded-circle"></div>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <p class="mb-2">
                                <b>Samantha</b> and <b>6 others</b> sent you <a href="#"
